column1: This file contains the velocity map parameters and stable surface errors for the glacier site described below.
Point of Contact: Jukes Liu; Boise State University; jukes.liu@gmail.com
Area of Interest = Sít' Kusá / Turner Glacier
sat = satellite platform (S2 = Sentinel-2, LS = Landsat, PS = PlanetScope)
data_percent = percentage of pixels within the glacier outline that contain data values [0 to 100]
err_vx = stable surface error for x-component of velocity [meters/year]
err_vy = stable surface error for y-component of velocity [meters/year]
err_v = stable surface error for speed [meters/year]
mid_date = date midpoint of the image pair [yyyy-mm-dd]
filename = name of the geotiff file containing the velocity maps
